title: 08/16: Wide Receivers Preview (Part Two) (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
We start by debating if the late-round value is better at RB or WR (2:30). Then it's straight into ADP beginning with the middle of Round 3 (5:30) with Doug Baldwin, Tyreek Hill, Amari Cooper and more ... Finishing up our MIN WR debate (14:38), getting into guys like Larry Fitzgerald, Juju Smith-Schuster (30:25), Allen Robinson, the CLE WRs (35:33) and the DET WRs (42:35) ... As we get into Round 7 and later, who stands out? The guys give their thoughts on Chris Hogan, Corey Davis, why they're not loving Sammy Watkins, Kenny Stills vs. Alshon Jeffery, etc. ...
